description: Thorne and Taylor discuss how they will go about telling Alexandria her mother is dead. Thorne and Taylor finally tell Alexandria about Darla’s death.  Ridge and Brooke stress over how they are going to keep up at work while Thorne is away.  Stephanie tells Phoebe, about her observation that Taylor was acting guilty at the funeral. Nick suggests that Donna be the new model for Brooke’s Bedroom. Brooke then gives Donna a few modeling tips. Nick tells Ridge he wants to set some ground rules about Ridge and Brooke’s interaction at work.  Ridge becomes angry.
